Package com.thingmagic

Class Gen2

java.lang.Object
com.thingmagic.Gen2
public class Gen2 extends Object
This class is a namespace for Gen2-specific subclasses of generic Mercury API classes, Gen2 data structures, constants, and Gen2 convenience functions.
